Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Foreign correspondents
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brrm
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Feb 1978
Foreign correspondents' views may be skewed if they stick to their capital city bases. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less